      <h1>Components for 
        Dynamic Hand Splinting</h1>
<p>Using prefabricated outriggers      simplifiies the fabrication of custom fit dynamic hand splints. Learn  about outriggers and sprint fabrication using the popular <em>Phoenix </em>components      and <em>Digitec.Base 2 </em>components online or with our <a href="instructions/index.html">video instructions.</a></p>
